title: BIP 34: Meme Competition for #WenDIGG
body:
TLDR;
• The Operations Team narrowed down the candidate list to a Top 16
• The Community will decide the ranking of the Top 16 entries
• Most voted entry will be declared the winner and remaining 2nd-10th will garner the consolation prizes.

Please vote for your top selection out of the 16. Contestants 11-16 are GIFs/videos, so please be sure to check those out via the links in the forum post below.

Discussions: https://forum.badger.finance/t/bip-34-meme-competition-for-wendigg/2728
